import React from 'react';
import ReactDom from 'react-dom'
import Card from './App'

ReactDom.render(
  <>
    <Card
      imgPoster="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611095567319-2f4c389168a9?ixid=MnwxMjA3fDF8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1951&q=80"
      title="Orignal photo of a Lady by DOCU SIGN"
      name="Lady"

    />
    <Card
      imgPoster="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1547656807-9733c2b738c2?ixid=MnwxMjA3fDF8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=634&q=80"
      title="Orignal photo of a Lady by DOCU SIGN"
      name="Lady"
    />
    <Card />

  </>,
  document.getElementById("root")
)
